</a></span></span></span></dir><h2 id="cl_2"> 3、<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/xiyiji/" target="_blank">洗衣机</a>槽清洁用泡腾片</h2><p itemprop="description">洗衣机滚轮隔一段时间就需要清洁一次，才能保证衣物更加干净卫生。拆卸清洁对于很多洗衣机都不可能实现，麻烦不说还很容易弄坏。</p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ax0x75g4/pic_4/' target='_blank'><img alt="见识下中国的家居智慧，这些设计虽小，但也太实用了吧！" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202008/06/5f2bd4938ed793543.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description">很简单一招是用洗衣机专用的清洁泡腾片，它的主要成分是碳酸氢钠和过氧化物，能够有效除菌，去污，建议每隔2月清洁一次，能降低家人皮肤敏感，衣服穿起来也更舒适。</p><dir><span class="embed-card main-site " style=""><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><a target="_blank" onclick="gtmAddToCart({'name':'洗衣机清洁片','id':'ax0x75g4' ,'dimension16':'','dimension19':'', 'price':'无','brand':'无' ,'mall':'淘宝精选', 'category':'无/无/无/无','metric1':'无','dimension10':'taobao.com','dimension9':'yuanchuang','dimension11':'无','dimension20':'无','dimension25':'无','dimension64':'yuanchuang'});if(typeof change_direct_url != 'undefined' && change_direct_url instanceof Function){change_direct_url(this)}" class=" res_smzdm" href="https://go.smzdm.com/d37c80ce9998f298/ca_bb_yc_1515_71001393_10111_0_55_0"  rel="nofollow" ><img ol  alt="见识下中国的家居智慧，这些设计虽小，但也太实用了吧！" class="res_smzdm" src="https://res.smzdm.com/images/card/taobao.png"/></a></span><span class="embed-card-info res_smzdm"><a target="_blank" onclick="gtmAddToCart({'name':'洗衣机清洁片','id':'ax0x75g4' ,'dimension16':'','dimension19':'', 'price':'无','brand':'无' ,'mall':'淘宝精选', 'category':'无/无/无/无','metric1':'无','dimension10':'taobao.com','dimension9':'yuanchuang','dimension11':'无','dimension20':'无','dimension25':'无','dimension64':'yuanchuang'});if(typeof change_direct_url != 'undefined' && change_direct_url instanceof Function){change_direct_url(this)}" class=" res_smzdm" href="https://go.smzdm.com/d37c80ce9998f298/ca_bb_yc_1515_71001393_10111_0_55_0"  rel="nofollow" ><span class="car